{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 69,
  "title": "第六十九章（玄用）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "用兵有言："
    },
    {
      "text": "吾不敢為主而為客，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不敢進寸而退尺。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂行無行，"
    },
    {
      "text": "攘無臂，"
    },
    {
      "text": "扔無敵，"
    },
    {
      "text": "執無兵。"
    },
    {
      "text": "禍莫大於輕敵。"
    },
    {
      "text": "輕敵，幾喪吾寶。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故抗兵相加，"
    },
    {
      "text": "哀者勝矣。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "陳用兵之道。老子疾時用兵，故託己設其義也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "主，先也。不敢先舉兵。客者，和而不倡。用兵當承天而後動。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "侵人境界，利人財寶，為進；閉門守城，為退。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "彼遂不止，為天下賊，雖行誅之，不成行列也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲大怒，若無臂可攘也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲仍引之，若無敵可仍也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "雖欲執持之，若無兵刃可持用也。何者？傷彼之民罹罪於天，遭不道之君，愍忍喪之痛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫禍亂之害，莫大於欺輕敵家，侵取不休，輕戰貪財也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "幾，近也。寶，身也。欺輕敵者，近喪身也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "兩敵戰也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "哀者慈仁，士卒不遠於死。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
